1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,500
The year was 1947. India stood on the edge of freedom.

2
00:00:03,501 --> 00:00:06,000
After centuries of British rule, the moment had arrived.

3
00:00:06,001 --> 00:00:09,000
August 15th, 1947 — India became an independent nation.

4
00:00:09,001 --> 00:00:12,500
Nehru addressed the nation at midnight with his iconic speech.

5
00:00:12,501 --> 00:00:15,500
"India will awake to life and freedom."

6
00:00:15,501 --> 00:00:18,000
Celebrations erupted across the country.

7
00:00:18,001 --> 00:00:21,500
But Partition brought heartbreak, violence, and loss.

8
00:00:21,501 --> 00:00:24,000
Millions migrated. Thousands perished.

9
00:00:24,001 --> 00:00:27,500
Still, hope endured. A new India began to rise.

10
00:00:27,501 --> 00:00:30,500
August 15th — India’s tryst with destiny had arrived.


